Class Identifier

java.lang.Object
  com.ibm.team.workitem.common.model.Identifier

public class Identifier
extends java.lang.Object

Identifier of an artifact of a particular type. Overwrites Identifier.equals(Object) and Identifier.hashCode() to implement value semantics.
